{"tid":83073,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"特區護照持有人將可免簽證前往白俄羅斯","createTime":"2017-01-16T12:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T22:40:44.000Z","uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2398abec98639f84add871082a17b1561a719d1c","tid":83073,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201701/16/P2017011600669.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201701%2F16%2FP2017011600669.htm&d=X2mAhVlg6XDRO7%2FRs9GaQWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c1f19303\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201701/16/P2017011600669.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官梁振英今日（一月十六日）下午在禮賓府與訪港的白俄羅斯第一副總理瓦西里．馬秋舍夫斯會面，就雙方共同關心的課題交換意見。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n梁振英感謝馬秋舍夫斯見證香港與白俄羅斯簽署全面性避免雙重課稅協定（協定），他指特區政府正積極配合國家落實「一帶一路」倡議，而白俄羅斯是「一帶一路」沿線國家，他期望協定能增強投資者信心，進一步擴大兩地的投資流動，促進香港與白俄羅斯的經貿關係。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>行政長官同時歡迎雙方達成共識，讓持有有效香港特區護照和有效白俄羅斯國民護照的訪客可享相互免簽證入境待遇，每次逗留不超過14天，為香港和白俄羅斯居民帶來更大方便，有助加強兩地旅遊、文化和經濟交流。雙方期望盡早完成相關程序，落實有關措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba63e6a850f0211478961aa1ee7ce96c48a7e3f2","tid":83073,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:39:57.000Z","msg":"明斯克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee9ab93bdf426502bca6d5ac998fa65c12b023d","tid":83073,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"去娶老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e750d1e45dffb61106a4356b1e0662e77bd37975","tid":83073,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"大家都是獨裁國家，不要分得那麼小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92794d6c1c22a313d319ebc34c2ab05e38532e98","tid":83073,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c